These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-8-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, grey, light-blue, green, azure, yellow, mauve
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: documentary, superhero, spy, crime, family, musical, martial-arts
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, folk, gospel, house, metal, rock, salsa
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, boat, skateboard, subway, taxi, tram, van
 1. the fan of folk is somewhere to the right of the fan of d&b##5
 2. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the fan of d&b##5
 3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 5. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
 7. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the person who likes grey##8
 8. the fan of house is not to the left of the person who likes grey##8
 9. the person watching crime movies is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
10. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person driving the bike##7
11. the person who likes grey is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
12. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
13. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the fan of metal##8
14. the person who likes azure is not the person driving the bike##6
15. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5
16. the person who likes blood-red is not to the left of the fan of d&b##8
17. the person who likes azure is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
18. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
19. the person who likes grey is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
20. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
21. the person driving the boat is on the left of the fan of rock##1
22. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person who likes yellow##8
23. the person who likes blood-red is the fan of metal##1
24. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
25. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
26. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
27. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
28. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the fan of folk and the person watching spy movies##7
29. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
30. the person driving the skateboard is the person who likes yellow##1
31. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
32. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
33. the person who likes mauve is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
34. the person who likes azure is not the person driving the tram##6
35. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5
36. the person who likes grey is not to the right of the person who likes yellow##8
37. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
38. the fan of metal is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8
39. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the person driving the tram##6
40. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5        |       6       |       7       |
| Color      | azure   | grey     | mauve    | blood-red      | yellow       | light-blue         | green |
| Movie-Genre           | documentary   | crime | superhero | family | musical | martial-arts | spy       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | house    | d&b    | metal    | folk           | salsa         | rock          |
| Transport     | van    | bike     | taxi   | tram     | skateboard     | boat          | subway        |

