.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-8-2::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, banana, cabbage, corn, lettuce, orange, plum
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: may, august, february, september, april, december, june
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: begonia, iris, dahlia, azalea, poppy, aconite, zinnia
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, bus, car, helicopter, motorbike, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
 6. the person eating orange is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person driving the bus##7
 7. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
 8. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 9. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
10. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
11. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
12. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
13. the person who growsaconite is somewhere between the person who growsiris and the person who growsdahlia##7
14. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
15. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
16. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
17. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
18. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
19. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
20. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
21. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
22. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the person who growsbegonia##8
23. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person eating banana and the person who growsdahlia##7
24. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the right of the person eating corn##5
25. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
26. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
27. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person eating plum##8
28. the person eating corn is the person driving the taxi##1
29. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
30. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
31. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
32. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
33. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
34. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |     4      |     5     |     6     |     7      |
| Food          | lettuce  | cabbage   | orange       | plum       | corn      | artichoke | banana     |
| Birthday           | december | september    | february | may  | june | august     | april    |
| Flower   | begonia   | iris | aconite      | poppy    | dahlia    | azalea    | zinnia     |
| Transport     | airplane | bus       | motorbike    | helicopter | taxi      | car       | snowmobile |

