.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-8-3::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  writer, accountant, security-guard, social-worker, journalist, engineer, bartender
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, daisy, lily, amaryllis, daffodil, bellflower
There are 7 different nationalities: american, australian, canadian, egyptian, german, russian, thai
7 different pets are kept: cat, dog, ferret, frog, goldfish, mouse, rabbit
 1. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
 2. the bartender is not to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##8
 3. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
 4. the american is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 5. the journalist is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
 6. the german is not the journalist##6
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the right of the egyptian##5
 8. the security-guard is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
10. the person who growsmarigold is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
11. the writer is between the person who growsbellflower and the social-worker##2
12. the canadian is not the bartender##6
13. the writer is somewhere between the australian and the social-worker##7
14. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
15. the security-guard is not to the right of the egyptian##8
16. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
17. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5
18. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the engineer##8
19. the german is not the person who growslily##6
20. the accountant is not to the left of the engineer##8
21. the thai is on the left of the egyptian##1
22. the person who growsiris is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8
23. the person who growslily is in an even position##4
24. the owner of the mouse is in an even position##4
25. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the social-worker##5
26. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
27. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
28. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the engineer##3
29. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the russian##1
30. the accountant is somewhere between the journalist and the canadian##7
31. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
32. the accountant is in an even position##4
33. the engineer is between the thai and the writer##2
34. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the australian##1
35. the person who growsamaryllis is in an even position##4
36. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the russian and the accountant##7
37. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the american##3
38. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5

.:: Answer ::.
